Package com.project1

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AddressBook
    Class that holds a collection of objects of the class AddressEntry Contains the methods to perform operations against the AddressEntry collection such as add, remove, readFromFile, list, find, and getAddressEntry
    AddressBookApplication
    Class that contains the main method to run the Address Book application.
    AddressBookApplicationTest
    Class to test AddressBookApplication class
    AddressBookTest
    Class to test AddressBook class
    AddressEntry
    Class that represents a single object entry in the AddressBook class Overrides a toString() method that prints out all the data of an entry and contains getters and setters to set and retrieve individual AddressEntry values.
    AddressEntryTest
    Class to test AddressEntry class
    Menu
    Class that contains the prompts used to interact with a user throughout the application.
    MenuTest
    Class to test Menu class
